# Local agent configuration for Codex CLI
AGENTS.md
papers/*
!papers/papers_doi.csv
!papers/SI_DOWNLOAD_STATUS.md
# Data layer for the Kemp-elimination corpus (JSON sidecars + rewritten
# markdowns). Tracks the deterministic outputs needed to re-run the
# extraction pipeline without re-invoking MinerU. Images and layout.json
# stay ignored (regeneratable, bulky).
!papers/_gold_standard/
!papers/_gold_standard/**
!papers/markdowns/
!papers/markdowns/**/
!papers/markdowns/**/main.md
!papers/markdowns/**/main.md.pre_rewrite
!papers/markdowns/**/paper_data.json
!papers/markdowns/**/tables_index.json
!papers/markdowns/**/*_content_list.json
papers/markdowns/**/images/
papers/markdowns/**/layout.json
.claude/skills/openspec-*/
openspec/
.codex/
design/
